{"tid":384242,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"無可否認，香港新生代最佳男歌手一定係坤哥","createTime":"2017-09-02T07:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T11:49:34.000Z","uid":129221,"like":5,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cee08a72607b0d1dc1cf7a8740e47edcfc811537","tid":384242,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T07:00:24.000Z","msg":"陽光點的歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 百聽不厭<br />\n這是陽光點的歌 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">one two three four</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EAvYkb9NAP4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEAvYkb9NAP4&d=V3zUvmTWh0Hw1QfT8m4wI49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=a6f6e16d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EAvYkb9NAP4</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">接近一千萬觀看次數</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一個人都應該聽左幾千次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來她不夠愛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個種毒男做兵感覺演繹得世界級 佢本人應該成日經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唱得好有感情 無呢啲遭遇都令人有親身體驗既感覺 聽佢幾分鐘既mv好似聽左一個毒男心碎既故事咁<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AphrA76OpnE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAphrA76OpnE&d=V3zUvmTWh0Hw1QfT8m4wI49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=c839c8a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AphrA76OpnE</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一千一百萬觀看次數</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩首千萬view既新生代歌手 除左gem根本無人比得上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望呢生人有機會見到gem同坤哥同台演出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n軒叔呢啲出親歌都無人知無人聽<br />\n更加唔好講乜鳩陳x宇 而我不知道陳x宇是誰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無人問津係因為佢係垃圾究竟連登仔幾時先明 不如試下好似的士陳咁北上發展算啦[sosad"},{"pid":"c058586e001a08d39fd95f01f8c62692a8ef369b","tid":384242,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:42:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b65abfd4ad1734fbfcc0d154110ef5fc10abadd","tid":384242,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f02ad3745fad5d71d90bfca612c502a236265e","tid":384242,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f539b58669a8127490b5d225c13efe0a78d88b7","tid":384242,"uid":95032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:01:43.000Z","msg":"邊個係坤哥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8485d172dc4c03092d3721665c1b1312ccd1e98","tid":384242,"uid":53730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:46:56.000Z","msg":"這是on9點的歌 這是傻閪點的歌"},{"pid":"6dab329ef8674d554889e54300d87a884df47baa","tid":384242,"uid":80943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:49:57.000Z","msg":"陳柏宇都唔識 好打極有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c8ac804de83a5385a1cacb7a00375517432405","tid":384242,"uid":141649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:37:44.000Z","msg":"棋"},{"pid":"233e255cfdb2b89ddd210a6e7e5c8e86a991f614","tid":384242,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T00:39:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>棋</blockquote><br />\n莫欺少年窮 人地已經發左圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c735d3259b226e4adf05fef2f1c7aec9ecb4bb37","tid":384242,"uid":129221,"like":0,